data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS HAVE BEEN RECEIVED! PLEASE HAVE ALL OFFERS IN BY 8PM, 9-28. From the perfect lot with no neighbors in front or back, the phenomenal curb appeal, 8 ft board on board fence to the custom in-ground gunite POOL in the back, this home has it all! Featuring an open floor plan, fresh interior paint, bamboo wood floors, upgraded light fixtures, gorgeous fireplace with stone, box window seating in the breakfast nook, windows under the kitchen cabinets, beautifully upgraded master bathroom and lots of natural light! You will LOVE relaxing in your pool on those hot summer days and nights! Enjoy the walking trails, ponds, amenity centers, and convenience of all three schools in the neighborhood!
